Invocation Name: daily sketch
des:
Want to be a good artist? You are looking at the right skill, Daily Sketch provides you a daily sketch / topic to challenge yourselves. If you are confused or ran out of topics or challenges to sketch / draw, dont worry ask Daily Sketch. Daily sketch will provide you a well curated topic which can challenge you and helps you to maintain true consistency on your drawing. 
First version supports Character drawing, let your imagination go wild..
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
